condition.narrative: The Recipient shall, not later than five (5) months after the Effective Date, cause ICASEES to recruit an external auditor, withterms of reference, qualifications and experience acceptable to the Association. (Schedule 2.I.A.4(c))
The Recipient shall, not later than five (5) months after the Effective Date, install a computerized accounting system. (Schedule2.II.B.4)

The Recipient shall, not later than three (3) months after the Effective Date, cause ICASEES to recruit a procurement specialist, afinancial management specialist, a project assistant and an assistant accountant, each with terms of reference, qualifications andexperience acceptable to the Association. (Schedule 2.I.A.4(b))

title.narrative: Statistical data sets are publicly disseminated online.
